    <div class=3D"cta-arrow">=E2=86=92</div>
    <div class=3D"cta-step"><div class=3D"num">3</div> Open Cowork</div>
    <div class=3D"cta-arrow">=E2=86=92</div>
    <div class=3D"cta-step"><div class=3D"num">4</div> Pick a folder and go=
</div>
  </div>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <div class=3D"footer">
    <div class=3D"footer-left">=C2=A9 2026 Lead with Impact. All rights res=
